description:
To search in Wikidata enter the keyword (default is 'wd') and your request after a space. You can also specify a language different from the default by adding to the keyword sign '-' and the language code.
Example 1: 'wd gnome' - look for the 'gnome' in Wikidata specified by default in the configuration of extension.
Example 2: 'wd-es gnome' - will look for the 'gnome' in the Spanish Wikidata.
Shortcuts:
<Super><Alt>w - to search from clipboard
<Super><Alt><Shift>w - to search from primary selection
name: Wikidata Search Provider
